api:
    http://localhost:3000/api/v1/detail_categories/:id
    用于获取某一个具体类别的所有商品列表
    类型: get
    参数: :id,整型，具体类别的id

返回结果格式如下：
{
  "result": 0,
  "detail_category": {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "222",
    "desc": "222"
  },
  "products": [
    {
      "name": "苹果",
      "images": [
        "http://dongfeng.qiniudn.com/uploads/image/image/4/1452914422.jpg",
